since you opened it or last saved your changes.

If you continue you will overwrite those changes.

Če nadaljujete, boste prepisali te spremembe.

column1: the tasklist containing the task is not active

column1: The uninstaller could not be run at this time.\n\nIf this was due to Windows SmartScreen, you may need to temporarily disable SmartScreen before trying again.

column1: The uninstaller could not be run at this time.\n\nPlease try again after your next reboot.

column1:
There was a problem updating ToDoList at this time.
Often this can be a problem with file and folder permissions.

Would you like to view the update log file for possible clues?

Trenutno je pri posodabljanju programa ToDoList prišlo do težave.
Pogosto je to lahko težava z dovoljenji datotek in map.

Ali želite ogledati datoteko dnevnika posodobitev za morebitne namige?

column1: ToDoList is updating your preferences. \nPlease wait...

ToDoList requires version 3 or later of the msxml component.

To update your version of this component, Google for 'msxml 3.0 download', 
and follow the relevant installation instructions. Then try again.

Če želite posodobiti svojo različico te komponente, kliknite na Google za 'msxml 3.0 download', 
in upoštevajte pomembna navodila za namestitev. Potem poskusite znova.
